STATE of North Carolina
v.
Tyrone HOLLEY. No. 533P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 3, 2005. Tyrone Holley, Pro Se. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, Michael Nifong, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 12th day of September 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Durham County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of November 2005."
